          - rid: 107151359355650071
          output: 'The masses are moved by our charity. Many among them had never
            received a gift in all their lives! We may take satisfaction in a righteous
            deed well done, with the added grace of new initiates joining our fold.

            [Gained
            10 Bliss & 20 Flock]

'
        - weight: 50
