          - rid: 107151359355650072
          - rid: 107151359355650073
          output: 'What a disaster! The delicacies were spoiled. Reports are already
            arriving of the commoners falling ill after consuming them. This is the
            price of placing our trust in outlanders! May they never receive the
            Gaze of the Beholder!

            [Lost 10 Bliss & 20 Flock]

'
